I_still_say_I_Love_You,
But_now_there's_no_reply.
I_always_feel_your_presence
As_if_you_never_left_my_side.
.

If_you_see_my_dad_in_Heaven
He_won't_be_hard_to_find.
He'll_be_the_one_to_greet_you_first,
For_he's_a_one-of-a-kind.
.

From_the_day_that_I_first_knew_you,
Your_heart_was_pure_and_kind;
Your_smile_was_sweet_and_innocent,
Your_wit_was_well_refined.
.

I_will_rise
After_every_fall.
I_will_rise
And_stand_tall.
.

Life_can_seem_an_endless_maze,
The_twists_and_turns,_lulls_and_delays,
But_things_always_fall_into_place...
In_good_time.
.

